{"tid":983542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門人：周街普通話　好陌生　呢度澳門黎架咩？","createTime":"2019-01-16T04:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T16:11:52.000Z","uid":47714,"like":148,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"8b8ca7fc5b6328d895b90984b58639e11adb29cf","tid":983542,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VenetianMacao/posts/10155984625293138/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FVenetianMacao%2Fposts%2F10155984625293138%2F&d=SX%2BUoBDMe9%2BAxfAiwDzPbI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=1aeebad7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/VenetianMacao/posts/10155984625293138/</a><br />\n<br />\nJenny K. Sio<br />\n阿婆講廣東話, 個孫講捲脷普通話, 你說悲不悲哀<br />\n阿婆都叫elegant, 個孫lao到不得了, 你說悲不悲哀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOscar Chao 點解要講普通話？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDavid Iao 卷晒脷咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nErica Leong 我想打個司機<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t8d/1/16/1f621.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft8d%2F1%2F16%2F1f621.png&h=4eaf53a8&s={SIZE}\" /> 點解要講普通話？！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChi Ian 深深體會到強國人已佔領澳門 半個澳門人我都睇唔到 包括司機都唔係本地 曲線宣傳？<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t1f/1/16/1f937_1f3fc_200d_2640.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft1f%2F1%2F16%2F1f937_1f3fc_200d_2640.png&h=21a529b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJeffrey Chan 一個關於澳門未來殘酷又寫實的故事 - 咸爺黎澳門之澳門冇澳門人 蛋撻唔係蛋撻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHeng Chan Chan<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/zG7Gyj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FzG7Gyj&h=2f3217a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWayne Lau 資拿味太濃，接撚受唔到囉<br />\n<br />\nLimin Zhang 滚出中国的土地澳门啦，滾返你的祖国越南吧😄<br />\n<br />\nWayne Lau Limin Zhang 滾你老母"},{"pid":"a09801f89ad9478f6dbcfc02df38cc67a7b1fec7","tid":98354